{"tid":1618523,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sim Card 上Lock 仲有Level 2","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T14:42:27.000Z","uid":211211,"like":204,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"7712988e0f86b69bd81b1d28788f79cc11e5f00e","tid":1618523,"uid":211211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"Level 1: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617953</a> 大家做左先!<br />\n<br />\n如果不幸被捕，有人會將你sim card 換去第二部機，再撞爆個你Sim Lock ， 於是會叫你入返PUK code 就可以重置Sim Lock。 <br />\n而取得PUK code 既方法，打上去CS hotline核對資料，佢地就會俾PUK code 你，Sim Lock 就會解鎖。<br />\n<br />\nLevel 2:<br />\n<br />\nOption 1: 落門市申請<br />\n任何人不得經CS hotline 對該電話號碼進行密碼重置，而是需要親身落門市認證<br />\n<br />\nOption 2: 落門市申請<br />\n如果經過CS hotline 查閱資料或重置密碼，需要於電話上入密碼認證<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就無人可以拎住你張身分證去取得PUK code。"},{"pid":"526122de6ff8e6414c5ced35e68e28dd026a7321","tid":1618523,"uid":35833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"推啊屌呢啲重要post就沉"},{"pid":"d6eb5b9e935d3633ecff814febda4a1805f55191","tid":1618523,"uid":249464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9c93c041678e835c9724328e480dca078b889f7","tid":1618523,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae18fdd4c5edf44b4db74b42cb326ff383f56289","tid":1618523,"uid":57042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:21:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbaf536f9be5f9022541ae6965368a0b69257187","tid":1618523,"uid":250170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6ab74bc429b7f8fd78ad03ca722067a56d91111","tid":1618523,"uid":111440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"開唔到level 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/no